N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 130.4 - Title, jurisdiction, and numbering of local laws

State Regulations

The filing form shall contain entries for the local
government that adopted the local law, the title and number of each local law
ascribed by the governing body of such local government. The Department of

State may assign additional numbering for indexing purposes. Such form shall
also contain entries for other information as may be required by
law. Notes
